        topic: "Kelonia Acquisition — $3.25B Upfront, Up to $7B Total",
        summary: "Lilly announced the acquisition of Kelonia Therapeutics on April 20 for $3.25B upfront, with up to $3.75B in additional milestone payments for a total potential deal of $7B. Kelonia is developing an in vivo CAR-T therapy for multiple myeloma — meaning it reprograms the patient\'s own T-cells inside the body rather than harvesting and engineering them externally. The deal is part of Lilly\'s stated strategy to diversify beyond GLP-1 drugs using the revenue they generate.",
